1. $(\forall x. P(x)) \vee \neg Q(y)$.

1. $\forall x. (P(x) \vee Q(y))$.

1. $(\forall x. P(x)) \vee (\exists x. Q(x))$.

1. $\forall x. (P(x) \vee Q(x))$.

